Use the standard library
This is how to is_prime of n:
   When n is less than 2, then:
      The answer is 0
   End when
   Remember that i is 2
   Do this n times:
      When i is at most n, then:
         Leave the loop
      End when
      When remainder of n and i is 0, then:
         The answer is 0
      End when
      Increase i
   End do
   The answer is 1
Now you know

>>> is_prime of 6
0
>>> is_prime of 101
1
>>> is_prime of 11
1